1. Getting Started:
   http://expressjs.com/starter/installing.html
   http://expressjs.com/starter/generator.html
2. Route
   http://expressjs.com/starter/basic-routing.html
   app.METHOD(PATH, HANDLER)
   http://expressjs.com/guide/routing.html
   -concepts:
   Router Path
   mountable router
   route handler
   app.route()
3. Static Middleware
   http://expressjs.com/guide/routing.html
   https://github.com/expressjs/serve-static?_ga=1.50793961.1942523044.1427357778
4. express configuration based on ENVIRONMENT
   refer to: Node.js in Action (chapter 9)
5. Configure view system:
   - the view directory
    app.set('views', path.join(__dirname, 'views'));
   - configure template engine
    app.set('view engine', 'jade');
   - enable view caching to reduce file I/O
6. express api: http://expressjs.com/4x/api.html
7. about middleware:
    - http://expressjs.com/guide/using-middleware.html
    - middleware list (优先选择第二个链接):
      https://github.com/senchalabs/connect?_ga=1.245697732.1942523044.1427357778#middleware
      http://expressjs.com/resources/middleware.html
    - different kinds/levels of middleware
    - app.use()
    - next()/next('route')
    - define error handler middleware last
8. use app.locals to manage application-level data or helper methods.
9. Resources: http://expressjs.com/resources/books-blogs.html


